                                    图书馆坚持“读者第一，服务至上”的办馆理念
                                </p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="carousel-item">
                            <img class="d-block w-100" src="~/Content/image/test-3.jpg" alt="Third slide">
                            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
